replies.body:
I used to play an MMORPG called Shaiya. I wanted a cool name, so I google translated "Magic". There were 2-3 different words, that I combined into "Praecano". "Venen" means Venom, or Poison. I don't remember the languages those words were from.

I recently started playing Shaiya again, and I played that character mostly. I noticed that I had an opportunity to change my name again, so I went from TheTNTPotato to PraecanoVenen.
